txt.en: While repelling the spiders in Cirith Ungol, you have encountered numerous clusters of eggs laid in the shadows of the tower. It is unknown if these are mere spider eggs or instead something far worse: a new brood of terror in Lhingris.\n\nYou should destroy any clusters of eggs in Cirith Ungol that you encounter.
Shelob's children have laid their vile eggs in the darkest corners of the Tower of Cirith Ungol.

You have destroyed many clusters of eggs in Cirith Ungol and have prevented Shelob and her children from bringing forth a new brood in Lhingris.
You have destroyed many clusters of eggs in Cirith Ungol.

Clusters of eggs can be found throughout Cirith Ungol, but primarily in the Tower of Cirith Ungol.\n\nWhile repelling the spiders in Cirith Ungol, you have encountered numerous clusters of eggs laid in the shadows of the tower. You should destroy them.
